 A blast came from the sky. As a shooting object landed in the forest. He 
merged from the pod. A destron. He stood up. A spider. His name charon. 
Kepper of the jailed back on the destron colony alpha 0. He had followed 
someone here. But what he callled himself now. Was remained to be seen.
